          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "LINAC"
                ],
                "institute": "1CANTMF"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Experiment performed at the ISAC I",
                "facility using TUDA detector array. Radioactive 18F",
                "beam was accelerated using RFQ/Linac of the ISAC 1",
                "facility."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Polyethylene (CH2)n target with thickness of (31.6 +-",
                "1.9)mu-g/cm2"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SISD"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Reaction products were detected by two",
                "silicon strip detectors (LEDA) and two double sided",
                "silicon strip detectors (S2)"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Measurement of scattered beam particles was",
                "achieved using a DE-E monolithic detector and a",
                "2mu-m aluminium shielded silicon photodiode. From",
                "this measurement beam intensity and beam",
                "purity  (i.e. 18-F/18-O ratio) was determined."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOF",
                "EDE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Reaction products identified combination of",
                "time of flight and E-dE methods."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COINC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The products of the 18F(p,a)15-O reaction",
                "were detected in coincidence"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "KINDT"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Production of the 18F radioactive beam was",
                "achieved using the ISOL method. An accelerated 500",
                "MeV beam of protons from the main cyclotron were",
                "directed onto a high power silicon carbide target to",
                "produce the 18F, which was then extracted and ionised",
                "using a FEBIAD ion source. The extracted beam was",
                "further accelerated to a pre-separator and then the",
                "mass separator where the 18F and isobaric elements were",
                "selected. From here the beam was post accelerated to",
                "the TUDA."
              ]
            }
          ],
